ggplot(serie_anual) +

  theme_linedraw()

Bar

ggplot(serie_anual) + 
  geom_col(aes(x=V1, y=V2)) + 
  labs(x='Ano', y=expression('Vazo (m'^3*'/s)')) + 
  theme_linedraw()

Histogram

N <- dim(serie_anual)[1] 
NC <- round(1 + 3.3 * log10(N))  # Sturges
ggplot(serie_anual) + 
  geom_histogram(aes(V2), bins=NC) + 
  labs(x=expression('Vazo (m'^3*'/s)'), y='Frequncia Absoluta') +
  theme_linedraw()

Frequency polygon

ggplot(serie_anual) + 
  geom_freqpoly(aes(V2), bins=NC) + 
  labs(x=expression('Vazo (m'^3*'/s)'), y='Frequncia Absoluta') +
  theme_linedraw()

Flow duration curve

vazao_decr <- sort(vazao, decreasing=TRUE) 
N <- length(vazao_decr) 
n <- c(1:N) 
n_N <- n / N
ggplot(serie_anual) + 
  geom_line(aes(x=n_N*100, y=vazao_decr)) + 
  labs(x='Permanncia (%)', y=expression('Vazo (m'^3*'/s)')) +
  theme_linedraw()
